LAST-MODIFIED:20260608T094134Z
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DESCRIPTION:In the Fishbowl\, Naomi gives Craig a lesson in chess. Dr. Blak
 e questions Blair. Nils gets a case of the yips\, forcing Martian to pivot
  to keep plans in play.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:aevum-tmdb-show-219971-s2e1@ph-tv-calendar
DTSTAMP:20260608T094134Z
SUMMARY:🍿 The Agency — S2E1: Kick the Wasp's Nest
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260621
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260622
LAST-MODIFIED:20260608T094134Z
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DESCRIPTION:Martian and Owen debrief Coyote. Bosko\, fearing a leak\, press
 ures Henry to clean house. Richardson turns up at the Chicken Coop with ne
 ws from Khartoum. Danny\, in Iran\, feels the ground move. Viking is escal
 ated to a category one.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:aevum-tmdb-show-219971-s2e2@ph-tv-calendar
DTSTAMP:20260608T094134Z
SUMMARY:🍿 The Agency — S2E2: A Bear in Wolf's Clothing
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260621
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260622
LAST-MODIFIED:20260608T094134Z
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DESCRIPTION:Confronted by Hassan\, Danny holds her ground. Bosko briefs the
  State Department with a dye-test as Henry sends Owen back into the field.
  Martian\, in search of an opening\, questions Naomi's objectivity. Richar
 dson promises Legoland a high value asset.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:aevum-tmdb-show-219971-s2e3@ph-tv-calendar
DTSTAMP:20260608T094134Z
SUMMARY:🍿 The Agency — S2E3: Spymaster
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260621
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260622
LAST-MODIFIED:20260608T094134Z
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DESCRIPTION:Martian exploits a means to an end as Henry breaks down the cha
 llenge to Bosko: drawing Viking out of Valhalla's territory. Hassan takes 
 Danny - and a Persian proverb - to heart. Dr. Blake lays groundwork with O
 wen. A call to Antwerp pays dividends.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:aevum-tmdb-show-219971-s2e4@ph-tv-calendar
DTSTAMP:20260608T094134Z
SUMMARY:🍿 The Agency — S2E4: Dead End
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260621
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260622
LAST-MODIFIED:20260608T094134Z
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DESCRIPTION:Dalaga pushes his luck with Richardson. Danny\, in Iran\, learn
 s grandmother is dead. Blair follows the money. Bosko and Henry talk game 
 plans in the Crisis Room as Owen takes a deep breath. Poppy treats Martian
  to a discourse on Kant.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:aevum-tmdb-show-219971-s2e5@ph-tv-calendar
DTSTAMP:20260608T094134Z
SUMMARY:🍿 The Agency — S2E5: Out Cold
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260621
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260622
LAST-MODIFIED:20260608T094134Z
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DESCRIPTION:A simple office miscommunication raises red flags in the Chicke
 n Coop. Bosko questions Henry's motives\, urging him to play risk versus r
 eward. Zayed reminds Sami who holds all the cards. Martian has a hunch as 
 Owen walks into the lion's den.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:aevum-tmdb-show-219971-s2e6@ph-tv-calendar
DTSTAMP:20260608T094134Z
SUMMARY:🍿 The Agency — S2E6: Officially a Ghost
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260621
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260622
LAST-MODIFIED:20260608T094134Z
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DESCRIPTION:Bosko is briefed on Snow White and the scope of Viking's game p
 lay. Sami\, trapped\, swallows her emotions. Naomi makes a difficult confe
 ssion. Down in the Matrix\, Henry narrows his focus as Martian looks to fi
 nd a Trojan Horse.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:aevum-tmdb-show-219971-s2e7@ph-tv-calendar
DTSTAMP:20260608T094134Z
SUMMARY:🍿 The Agency — S2E7: Drown Him Then Throw Him a Lifejacket
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260621
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260622
LAST-MODIFIED:20260608T094134Z
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DESCRIPTION:Henry's suspicions reveal hidden treachery. Simon and Blair unc
 over a loose cannon in Antwerp. Bosko sets his sight on a strategic flip a
 s Martian\, in his element\, offers up a lifejacket. In Bahrain\, Craig's 
 pitch to Popeye yields unexpected intel.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:aevum-tmdb-show-219971-s2e8@ph-tv-calendar
DTSTAMP:20260608T094134Z
SUMMARY:🍿 The Agency — S2E8: False Flag Attack
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260621
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260622
LAST-MODIFIED:20260608T094134Z
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DESCRIPTION:A stealth move in Bahrain pays dividends. Nils pitches De Bruyn
 e a plan that could solve all their problems. Dr. Blake challenges Naomi o
 n her camouflage. Meanwhile\, Osman accepts his fate as\, outside the Univ
 ersity\, Danny is met with a shock.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:aevum-tmdb-show-219971-s2e9@ph-tv-calendar
DTSTAMP:20260608T094134Z
SUMMARY:🍿 The Agency — S2E9: Rogue Cell
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260621
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260622
LAST-MODIFIED:20260608T094134Z
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DESCRIPTION:A cryptic message leads Poppy to reach out to Dozer. Henry caut
 ions Naomi to not jump too soon. At the Chicken Coop\, Richardson drops a 
 bombshell on Bosko. Meanwhile\, Viking delivers a message as Danny fights 
 to give nothing away.
END:VEVENT
